fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "hotdoc_markdown/gtkwidget.html#gtk_widget_new", "fragment": "gtk_widget_new \nThis is a convenience function for creating a widget and setting its properties in one go. For example you might write gtk_widget_new GTK_TYPE_LABEL label Hello World xalign NULL to create a left aligned label. Equivalent to g_object_new but returns a widget so you don t have to cast the object yourself. \nParameters \ntype ID of the widget to create \nname of first property to set \nvalue of first property followed by more properties NULL terminated \na new GtkWidget of type widget_type \n"});